      </div>

      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head>
        <p> Very similar to <xref type="inscription" n="175" href="010190">1.190</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="177" href="020528">2.528</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="178" href="010191">1.191</xref>; see discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="IX.45">IX.45</xref>.</p>
      </div>

